snippet.textDisplay: Finally, our beloved Coke Studio is out, and what a marvellous way to welcome the new season through a Sindhi song 🎉🎉🎉 The authenticity and real emotions make the song a real feast to hear and watch. Not a Sindhi, but proud to be a part of a journey into the heart of Sindhi culture through this beautiful song. Hats off to all the singers, musicians, directors, people behind the camera, but mostly to Xulfi for believing in it and bringing it for the joy of the whole world. Love and respect from Australia 🇦🇺
